Package oogasalad.editor.controller.listeners

Class EditorListenerNotifier

java.lang.Object
oogasalad.editor.controller.listeners.EditorListenerNotifier
public class EditorListenerNotifier extends Object
Manages and notifies EditorViewListeners about changes in the editor state. This class centralizes notification logic, decoupling it from the main controller.
